Chapter 2:  General Information and Sign-ups.

If you want more information about the tournament, pick up a copy
of the book titled "Tournament Leaflet".  Event Schedules will
be posted on the Tournament Board.  Other information and answers to
common questions can be found on the tournament bulletin board or you can
ask questions of the tournament organizers by using the <h> mail system. 
Post any and all <h> mail to "Fay".  <h> mail is important since
all sign-ups will be done by <h> mail to "Fay".  For other sign-up
mechanisms look at the tournament board. 

